.TH LPF-POLICY-TESTS 5 "June 2026" "lpf 0.1.1" "lpf Manual"
.SH NAME
lpf\-policy\-tests \- policy assertion fixture format
.SH DESCRIPTION
Policy tests describe expected pass, drop, reject, NAT, route, queue, log, and table behavior.
The fixture format is planned as an OCaml\-validated schema used by lpf test and CI.
.SH EXAMPLES
from: 10.0.0.5
to: 1.1.1.1
proto: tcp
port: 443
expect: pass
.SH SEE ALSO
lpf\-test(8), lpf\-explain(8)
